03:21.377 --> 03:23.745
- David worried?
- He wants to be.

03:23.746 --> 03:26.481
What's he done this past year?
Signed a proper load of fucking turkeys.

03:26.482 --> 03:29.250
This new Rage album wants
to make ABBA's Greatest Hits

03:29.251 --> 03:31.083
sound like Sonic fucking Youth
or he's finished.

03:31.987 --> 03:32.955
Fucking nasty.

03:33.122 --> 03:34.818
