03:35.391 --> 03:36.586
What, Head of A&R?

03:41.263 --> 03:42.356
They might offer it to you.

03:43.032 --> 03:45.592
No. No, you've got...

03:48.871 --> 03:50.066
...you know, seniority.

03:51.840 --> 03:53.433
Right, I'll get the drinks in.

03:55.010 --> 03:57.111
Last year, 1996,

03:57.112 --> 04:01.616
